Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.23,0:00:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.65,0:00:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.65,0:00:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.48,0:00:06.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:06.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.86,0:00:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.11,0:00:15.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:15.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.91,0:00:22.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:22.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.87,0:00:26.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:26.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.13,0:00:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
