Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.12,0:01:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多美好的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道派大星在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Patrick's at home
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.13,0:01:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hiya, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watcha doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到珊迪家去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going over to Sandy's place
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.51,0:01:18.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:18.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.14,0:01:20.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意看着不像是珊迪家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:20.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look like Sandy's place
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.14,0:01:22.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们先别急
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:22.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't lose your barnacles, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.89,0:01:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.27,0:01:26.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:26.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.56,0:01:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.19,0:01:29.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:29.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Texas"?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥叫德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's a Texas?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就只是个念想了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's nothing but a memory now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.53,0:01:37.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:37.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, then
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.03,0:01:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来做你的树屋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's make one of your tree dome
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.32,0:01:40.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实  我突然就
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:40.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y-You know, all of a sudden
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不想堆沙堡了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l don't feel much like sandcastles, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see y'all later
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.87,0:01:45.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:45.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.84,0:01:51.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:51.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在没心情玩空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'm just not feeling up to karate right now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没心情玩空手道是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Not feeling up to karate," huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你怎么说  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可真希望珊迪没从背后偷袭我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, I hope Sandy doesn't attack me from behind
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.48,0:02:15.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:15.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来冲浪了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surf's up, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.82,0:02:18.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:18.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.16,0:02:25.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:25.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, there's nothing like going jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪你看  我们捉到一只了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Sandy, we caught one
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.34,0:02:37.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我没心情堆沙堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:37.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right now, I don't want to build sandcastles
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩空手道  还有吃水母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,play karate or eat jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.34,0:02:41.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不会吃水母的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:41.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't eat 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会放水母走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We let 'em go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞吧  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fly away, little critter
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去吧  回到属于你的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on, go back home where you belong
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去吧  回到你家人和朋友身边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run along, back to your family and friends
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们一定很想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know they miss you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也一定很想念它们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as much as you miss them
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁它们没落下你  尽快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, before they forget you and leave you behind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.57,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 苏格兰民歌《可爱的家》(Home Sweet Home) ]
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的家庭真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no place like home
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你到底是在哭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, what the heck are you crying about?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.84,0:03:16.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没哭  只是头盔漏水了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:16.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l ain't cryin', my helmet just sprung a leak
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该只是有一点想家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just feeling a little homesick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想家是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Homesick, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad-gum it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Da, ta-dah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.31,0:03:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想不通  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能只有松鼠才懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just a squirrel thing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.42,0:04:02.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿我回到德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:02.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wish I was back in Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.38,0:04:07.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大海不是松鼠的家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:07.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ocean's no place for a squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿回德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wish I was in Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.81,0:04:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世上最美的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prettiest place in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哦不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想在我内心深处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess a-deep in my heart
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我将永远是个德克萨斯女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll always be a Texas girl
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.07,0:04:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to go ho-o-o-o-ome
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ho-ome
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, listen to that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快弄下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get 'em off me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.09,0:04:43.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:43.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.18,0:04:45.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:45.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想在德克萨斯醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to wake up in Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.27,0:04:56.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怀念那开阔天空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:56.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I miss those wide-open skies
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怀念我广阔田野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I miss my 20 acres
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.57,0:05:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤肉和山核桃派
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barbecues and pecan pies
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, why
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,距离德州千万里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I'm so far from you, Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.41,0:05:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我仅能黯然神伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I can do is cry
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(294.803,451.333)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.72,0:05:40.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:40.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to go ho-o-o-ome
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得她是不是知道松饼人之歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think she knows the muffin man song?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  她是发自内心唱出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, she sang that song from her heart
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她真的很想念德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She really misses Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那咱就去弄点德克萨斯过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go get some Texas and bring it down here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you can't
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.67,0:06:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你的天分发功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, your genius is showing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.09,注释,,0,0,0,,[ genius（天分）与 genital（私处）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318.814,400.667)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都很完美的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything looks perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要去带珊迪来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to go get Sandy now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干快点  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, hurry it up, lads
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能一直这样占用蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't squat like this forever
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪的惊喜在蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's surprise is at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到她看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait till she sees the
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要破坏惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't spoil the surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要跟我们一起来蟹堡王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to come with us to the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你大包小包的要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with those bags?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要回德克萨斯老家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm goin' back home to Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, we
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该让我这颗风滚草滚回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for this tumbleweed to tumble on home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.09,0:06:43.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:43.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.88,0:06:44.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:44.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.00,0:06:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我们要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause we were gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王那边要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at the Krusty Krab is
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个方向不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that is not the right direction
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.09,0:06:50.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我没法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:50.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lf I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你走之前的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't want to leave
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好先到蟹堡王吃个蟹黄堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without having one last Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我鱼食吃腻了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of fish food, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是珊迪  你就不想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,B-But Sandy, don't you want to
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到蟹堡王跟你朋友道个别吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,say good-bye to all your friends down at the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't do that, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样会很伤感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'd be too sad
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,N-No, no, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她居然就这么走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱智德克萨斯有什么好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so great about dumb, old Texas?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱智德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Texas is dumb?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辱德克萨斯者  后果自负
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare take the name of Texas in vain
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以不能说弱智德克萨斯的坏话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean we can't say anything bad about dumb, old Texas?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you can't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.81,0:07:40.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那能不能说德克萨斯人弱智
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:40.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, can we say people from Texas are dumb?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是不准说德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't say nothin' about Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.19,0:07:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说我们不能辱  德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we shouldn't say anything bad about Tex-as
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我警告你了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Texas, too
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.17,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自民谣"Git Along Little Doggies" ]
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快狗吧  小走们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a dog, little longie
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快狗吧  小走们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a dog, little longie
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a dog
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们最好给我住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,y'all best cut it out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:17.76,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自民谣"Deep in the Heart of Texas" ]
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.22,0:08:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夜空的星辰黯淡无光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The stars at night are dull and dim
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每当它们被迫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whenever they have to be
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照耀在弱智德克萨斯上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over dumb, old, stupid Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我现在是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, what am I now?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱智
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错  我是德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这有啥区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the difference
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们最好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You all best apologize
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,否则我就要对你们不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'm going to be on you like ugly on an ape
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先抓到我们再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have to catch us first
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.24,0:08:40.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:40.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got her
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王  我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab, here we come
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.12,0:08:48.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能不能说德克萨斯的植物很弱智
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:48.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we say that plants from Texas are dumb?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.67,0:08:54.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能不能说德克萨斯的鞋子很弱智
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:54.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we say that shoes from Texas are dumb?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, that's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.51,0:09:01.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你以为那个慢老婆子德克萨斯会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:01.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think that old slowpoke, Texas, is gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再跑快点  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run faster, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我收回你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to take back what you said
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(278.796,488.667)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是在惹牛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You been messin' with the bull
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在牛角要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now here come the horns
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(548.254,310)}德克萨斯快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a party
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.85,0:10:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你办的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我办的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你专属的一小部分德克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's your own little slice of Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.81,0:10:27.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看一下吧  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:27.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check it out, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有方块舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got square dancin'
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超大烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,giant barby-q's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(783.089,920)}刺 {\fnArial}Q
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(751.015,915.333)}山 核 桃
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手工豆罐头派
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Homemade peas-in-a-can pies
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(751.015,630)}豆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(916.425,918)}十    加    仑
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有我们专属的宽边高顶帽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we got our very own ten-gallon hats
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要留下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gonna stay?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要再哭了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't cry anymore, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去帮你拿行李
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go get your bags
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not cryin'
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是喜极而泣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm laughin'
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很感谢你们做的事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I appreciate what y'all are trying to do, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.10,0:11:15.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家的真谛并非烤肉还有山核桃派
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:15.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but home isn't about barbecues and pecan pies
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Home is where you're surrounded
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有很多关照你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by other critters that care about you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Duh, what am I doin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都在家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I been home all along
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到现在才想明白这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I took me till just now to realize it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你要留下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you'll stay?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm stayin'
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's stayin'
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我好想摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That makes me feel all wiggly
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.22,0:11:42.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要弱智德克萨斯干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:42.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, who needs dumb, old Texas?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该开始跑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should I start running now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.39,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无地自容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.52\pos(254.777,380.667)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:57.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1094.478,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.52\pos(410.778,702.667)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:57.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.3\pos(415.408,312.667)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.46\pos(252.666,280.666)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.46\pos(410.072,629.999)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1033.23,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(677,208)}欢迎来到酷乐湖
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.46,0:12:16.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海滩游客都听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:16.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, beachgoers
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这是非法闯入此地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are trespassing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.55,0:12:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有十七分钟的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have exactly 17 minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.13,0:12:24.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挪走你们的死尸  因为这里即将建造
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:24.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to haul your carcasses off of the future site
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之超级霸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the Chum Bucket Mega Bucket
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1001.798,283.333)}超级霸未来选址
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(772.358,848.667)}救生员
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行  随你们的便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, have it your way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不介意铲平你们所有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't mind bulldozing over each and every one
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy, look
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人在这放了个玩具卡车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody left this toy tractor here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放下去  比利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put that down, Billy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面有细菌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That has germs on it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.28,0:12:48.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:48.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.41,0:12:51.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:51.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll see
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll all see
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之超级霸的未来选址
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The future site of the Chum Bucket Mega Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.79,0:13:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能被这些白痴海滩游客占走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,must be cleared of these cretinous beachgoers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可事实越来越明显了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's becoming increasingly obvious
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不能否认了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can deny it no longer
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am small
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要有个大个的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need someone big
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.64,0:13:15.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我清空这片海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:15.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to clear the beach for me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.32,0:13:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踏上沙滩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steppin' on the beach
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踏上沙滩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steppin' on the beach
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.15,0:13:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踏上沙滩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steppin' on the beach
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.28,0:13:26.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踏上沙滩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:26.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steppin' on the beach
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是我要找的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's the one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:39.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1049.82,790)}冰淇淋
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.87,0:13:35.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:35.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来两份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two please
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.04,0:13:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.54,0:13:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来一份冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, please
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来一份冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, please
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.76,0:13:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都卖光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're all out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why are you crying?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.98,0:14:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哭是因为我买了俩冰淇淋甜筒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'm crying because I've got these two ice cream cones
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我只要一个而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I only need one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另外一个不知道要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do with the other one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你把其中一个甜筒吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll eat one of those ice cream cones for you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.59,0:14:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你真会帮我吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, would you do that for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.51,0:14:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.06,0:14:39.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:39.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.49,0:14:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要的东西到手了感觉不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lsn't it great to get the things you desire?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.61,0:14:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就比如说刚刚那个甜筒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like that ice cream cone, for instance
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.33,0:14:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要稍微再训练一下就能要啥有啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can have anything you want with a little training
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.42,0:14:59.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,训练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:14:59.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Training?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.08,0:15:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得学会更加坚定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just have to learn to be more assertive
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I can show you how
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚定是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Assertive, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要啥有啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything I want?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds great
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妙极了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wonderful
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他别坐你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let that guy sit on you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚定第一课
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Assertiveness lesson number one
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫他下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell him to get off
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你坐到我身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y-you're sitting on my body
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐的地方也是我的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which is also my face
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了  要坚定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, be assertive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.47,注释,,0,0,0,,[ assert（坚定）与 insert（插入）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是乱插
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not insertive
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你错过时机了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you missed your chance
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要霸道才能得到想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to be aggressive to get the things you want
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你心太软了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're too soft
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.32,0:16:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我是海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm a spong
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't say it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是抢走了你冰淇淋的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's the guy who took your ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不想要回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you want it back?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我朋友有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My friend's got something to say
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快骂他  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell him off, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让自己坚定起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Assert yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我的冰淇琳甜筒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my ice cream cone
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.05,0:16:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他尝尝厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let him have it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can have it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给你示范
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个铅笔脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, pencil-neck
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我滑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slither over here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交出那个冰淇淋甜筒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surrender that ice cream cone
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.31,0:16:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,否则你所有清醒的时刻都将化为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or every waking moment for you will become
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,充斥着痛苦的漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a swirling torrent of pain and misery
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guy was crying
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他那是喜极而泣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those were tears of joy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他为你学会了坚定而感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was happy that you were assertive
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.33,0:17:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下知道发起疯来有多美好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see how wonderful life can be when you're maniacal?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是叫坚定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought it was called assertive
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.05,0:17:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是坚定能让我有这个冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it got me this ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then I like it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找到东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found something
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我金属探测器坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, my metal detector broke
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能借用下你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I use yours?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的下一课
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your next lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be aggressive
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫那人滚远点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell that guy to take a hike
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要跟我去远足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take a hike with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看你现在干的什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now look what you've done
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫那人掉沟里去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell that guy to go fall in a ditch
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到沟里去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, go check in that ditch
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,埋藏的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wow Buried treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见了没  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you see that, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那人发现了埋藏的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guy found some buried treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你怎么做都做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you'll never get it right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他说你会空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell that guy you know karate
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.64,0:18:02.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不还金属探测器就给他绑成结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you'll tie him in a knot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you don't get your metal detector back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不还金属探测器  我就给你绑鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tie your shoe if you don't give that back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我穿的是凉鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm wearing sandals
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.11,0:18:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他穿的是凉鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's wearing sandals
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.62,0:18:20.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:20.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是开始觉得我这是在浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to think that this is a waste of time
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's not
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.87,0:18:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你多半没有顶天立地所需要的素质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you don't have what it takes to be a standup guy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是飞机餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what about airline food?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞机餐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Airline food
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.21,0:18:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  这菜怎么搞的那么难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My gosh, what is up with that stuff?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.01,0:18:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(884.409,920)}顶  天  立  地
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  我可以演单口喜剧的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, I can be a standup guy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.14,0:18:40.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:40.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你绝对没法要啥有啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you'll never get what you want
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.51,0:18:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你老是让别人践踏你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You always let people step all over you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟楼梯差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just like stairs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再给我一次机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,give me another chance
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以  不过这是你最后一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, but this is your last chance
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.40,0:18:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看那些霸占海滩的人晒着你的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all those beach hogs soaking upyour sun rays
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你拥有美黑所需要的素质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have what it takes to get a tan?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just watch me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.33,0:19:12.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  这玩意好多沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:12.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, this thing is sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.51,0:19:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  我的计划开始起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, my plan is beginning to work
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们都离开海滩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're leaving the beach
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, that was wonderful
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是把全身都晒了一遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that an all-over tan?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不算全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, not all of me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(780.362,235.333)}零食吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot dogs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.36,0:19:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看热狗摊前边的那条长队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that huge line at the hot dog stand
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚定起来  插到前边去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Assert yourself to the front
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以更上一层楼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do better than that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go home
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  真是太天才了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, that was genius
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.79,0:19:54.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看那些放风筝的挡了你视野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:54.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all those kite-flyers blocking your view
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挡了你的风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breaking your wind
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  把球扔给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, throw us the ball
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要咋办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just go home, I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  你看见了没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, did you see that?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是合格的大哥大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was a regular alpha male
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  我的坚定把大家都赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, all my asserting has driven everybody away
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没跟我说过大家会走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't tell me everyone would leave
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:49.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(903.085,259.333)}超级霸未来选址
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级霸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mega bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.43,0:20:53.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你利用我开发土地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:53.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You used me for land development
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wasn't nice
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没想明白吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Haven't you figured it out, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好人没好报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice guys finish last
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.40,0:21:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有霸道的人才能征服世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only aggressive people conquer the world
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,霸道的好人会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what about aggressively nice people?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:22.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(951.108,235.333)}零食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(887.078,718)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(887.078,718)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睫毛刷冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Butterfly kisses
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can't take it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too cute
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太  太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's, it's disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.45,0:21:51.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:51.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我新冲浪板触礁了  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hit a reef with my new board, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题不大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.33,0:22:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Killer
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.67,0:22:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.09,0:22:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Before it's too late
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的好心好意把大家都带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your kindness is bringing everybody back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.43,0:22:16.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:16.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.06,0:22:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卡哇邦嘎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cowabunga
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.90,0:22:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.32,0:22:29.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:29.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was awesome
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.16,0:22:34.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸的事我很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:34.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about the Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.79,0:22:36.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管海之霸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:36.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget about that
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是没办法一口气接受这么多好意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't take so much kindness at one sitting
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.38,0:22:42.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:42.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Need
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.00,0:22:43.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:43.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hatred
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.46,0:22:48.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想打排球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:48.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Volleyball, anyone?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.51,0:22:49.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:49.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.59,0:22:50.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:50.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Service
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.73,0:23:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.90,0:23:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.82,0:23:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.07,0:23:08.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:08.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.86,0:23:11.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:11.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense is something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.11,0:23:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.87,0:23:15.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:15.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.33,0:23:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.71,0:23:26.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:26.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.21,0:23:35.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:35.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
